{"title": "SINGER 4411 Heavy Duty Sewing Machine With Accessory Kit & Foot Pedal - 69 Stitch Applications + SINGER Bobbin Winder - for Class 15 & 15J Bobbins - Battery Powered with Included Power Adapter", "bullet_points": "SINGER HEAVY DUTY SEWING MACHINE: It has 11 Built-in Stitches- 6 Basic Stitches, 4 Decorative Stitches, 1 Built-in Buttonhole—perfect for crafts, home decor, fashion sewing and much more
SEWING TIME-SAVER: Never unthread your sewing machine to wind a bobbin again! This sewing game changer is an external bobbin winder that quickly and easily fills bobbins with thread. The SINGER Universal Bobbin Winder is a great sewing and crafting project time saver.
Full Metal Frame - This internal rigid metal support keeps your machine stable and helps ensure long lasting durability.
BOBBIN WINDING MADE EASY: With the one-touch auto winding system, bobbins are filled quickly and easily. Easy set-up with thread guides will have you winding a bobbin within seconds.
Extra High Sewing Speed - Sew up to 1,100 stitches per minute for extra speed when you need it. Great for larger projects with long seams and seam finishes.
AUTO SHUT-OFF: The auto shut-off feature automatically stops the bobbin winding when the bobbin is full.
Four-Step Buttonhole - Buttonholes are sewn in four easy steps, clearly displayed on the Stitch Selector Dial, with consistent results every time.
PORTABLE COMPACT BOBBIN WINDER:The Universal Bobbin Winder is conveniently housed within a compact and portable case, making it easy to store, use at home, or on-the-go! Either use the included power cord or three AA batteries (not included). Includes two spindles for extra bobbin storage.
Top Drop-In Bobbin With Clear View Cover - Jam-proof bobbin and clear bobbin cover plate are both transparent, making it easy to monitor your thread supply. The bobbin is easy to wind and easy to insert as well.
BOBBIN COMPATIBILITY: Compatible with Class 15 and 15J Bobbins.", "description": "With 50% more power and enhanced speed, the SINGER® Heavy Duty 4411 brings professional sewing results without breaking the bank. The 69 Stitch Applications include basic, stretch, and decorative sewing techniques, perfect for all types of fabrics. From canvas to denim, the Heavy Duty 4411 will be your go-to sewing tool for thick fabrics or layers. Sewing sheer or lightweight fabrics? No problem! The easily adjustable presser foot pressure makes sewing very lightweight fabrics a breeze.

Whether you're creating home decor or mending jeans, you will love having this true workhorse, the SINGER® Heavy Duty 4411, by your side!

Dimensions & More Info:
Plastic & Metal material
15” x 6.25” x 12” (machine); 18” x 8.5” x 13” (carton)
14.6 lbs
Watts (84); Volts (120); Hz (60)
Made In Vietnam

Say good-bye to the days of having to unthread your sewing machine in the middle of a project, just to wind a bobbin. Meet the customer-inspired SINGER® Universal Bobbin Winder– a must-have for every busy sewist-on-the-go! This sewing game changer is an external bobbin winder that quickly and easily fills bobbins with thread. It keeps you from having to unthread your sewing machine to fill a bobbin, then re-thread the machine again! With the one-touch auto winding system, bobbins are filled quickly and easily. The auto shut-off feature automatically stops the winding when the bobbin is full. It also includes two spindles for additional bobbin storage. The Universal Bobbin Winder is conveniently housed within a compact and portable case, making it easy to store, use at home, or wind bobbins on-the-go! Either use the included power cord or three AA batteries (not included). Whether you need to wind a bobbin that’s low on thread or change your bobbin thread color in a jiffy, the SINGER® Universal Bobbin Winder is your go-to bobbin-filling partner!", "product_type": "SEWING_MACHINE", "category_root": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "category_sub": "Bobbins", "color": "", "size": "", "material": "Metal", "style": "Sewing Machine + SINGER Bobbin Winder", "target_audience": "", "specific_uses": "", "model": "4411", "item_form": "", "number_of_items": "", "included_components": ""}

EMBELLISHMENT FEET: In addition to the 8 feet that come in the SE700 box, this embroidery bundle also comes with 5 specialty feet: stitch in the ditch, roller foot, piping foot, edge joining foot and gathering foot bundle", "description": "Take your sewing and embroidery skills to the next level with the Brother SE700 computerized sewing and embroidery machine. Equipped with a generous workspace and a stylish yet modern cosmetic, the SE700 has 135 built-in embroidery designs, 10 built-in embroidery fonts, over 103 built-in sewing stitches, and 10 styles of one-step auto-size buttonholes. In addition, the SE700 has a sharp 3.2 x 1.8” LCD display that allows for easy on-screen editing for all your DIY projects. When connected to a wireless network (wireless LAN enabled), the SE700 is compatible with Design Database Transfer (no USB required) that allows you to send files from your PC to your machine so you can send and then stitch! A creative mobile app called the Artspira App lets you download embroidery patterns to the SE700 and allows you the ability to create embroidery patterns by drawing on your mobile device. The SE700 comes with an advanced needle threading system and an automatic thread cutter, sewing speeds up to 710 spm, and compatibility with the Brother iBroidery platform for even more inspiration. Creating your next customized project can be effortless with a 6.4" x 4.0" work area and a maximum embroidery area of 4" x 4", so making children's clothes, doing minor apparel repairs, and even creating warm home decor can be achieved. Creating your next customized project can be effortless with a 6.4" x 4.0" work area and a maximum embroidery area of 4" x 4", so making children's clothes, doing minor apparel repairs, and even creating warm home décor can be achieved.
